20:58.959 --> 21:01.668
I pronounce you
husband and wife.

21:02.869 --> 21:04.805
Go on and do your thing.

21:13.013 --> 21:14.214
Hey, mama, you in there?

21:14.280 --> 21:16.349
[chuckling]
Yes.

21:16.416 --> 21:19.352
[congregation cheering]

21:24.157 --> 21:25.792
(Reverend Taylor)
Ladies and gentlemen,
welcome

21:25.859 --> 21:29.395
Mr. and Mrs.
Overton Wakefield Jones.

